                <spanspec namest="1" nameend="7" spanname="s1t7" align="center"/>
                <thead>
                    <row>
                        <entry colspan="7" spanname="s1t7" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold">SPOTLIGHT</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                </thead>
                <tbody valign="top">
                    <row>
                        <entry colname="1" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold"></emph>
                                <emph type="bold">STEP</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="2" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold"></emph>
                                <emph type="bold">KEY</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="3" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold"></emph>
                                <emph type="bold">ACTION</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="4" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold">TEST POINTS</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="5" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold"></emph>
                                <emph type="bold">SPEC.</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="6" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold">YES - IN SPEC.</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="7" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para>
                                <emph type="bold"></emph>
                                <emph type="bold">NO - OUT OF SPEC.</emph>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry colname="1" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para>1.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="2" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para>Off</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="3" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para>Remove fuse F1-D and check for open condition.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="4" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para>F1-D.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="5" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para>&#60;1 ohm?</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="6" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para>Go to next step.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="7" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para>Locate cause of overload condition and replace fuse.</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry colname="1" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para>2.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="2" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para>Off</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="3" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para>At F1-D measure voltage from circuit 14Y to ground.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="4" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para>F1-D 14Y to gnd.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="5" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para>12&#177;1.5 volts?</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="6" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para>Go to next step.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="7" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para>Locate cause of low or no voltage in circuit 14Y or 14H from battery stud B2, then
                                repair.
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry colname="1" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para>3.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="2" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para>Off</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="3" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para>With fuse re-installed, disconnect connector (428), and at circuit 63P measure voltage
                                to gnd.
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="4" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para>(428) 63P to gnd.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="5" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para>12&#177;1.5 volts?</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="6" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para>Go to next step.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="7" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para>Locate cause of low or no voltage in circuit 63P, then repair.</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry colname="1" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para>4.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="2" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para>Off</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="3" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para>Reconnect connector (428) and disconnect left spot light at circuit 64H. At 64H
                                measure voltage to gnd.
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="4" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para>64H to gnd.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="5" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para>12&#177;1.5 volts?</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="6" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para>Go to next step.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="7" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para>Locate cause of low or no voltage in circuit 64H, 64E or 63P then repair.</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry colname="1" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para>5.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="2" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para>Off</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="3" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para>Repair or replace left spotlight and switch assembly.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="4" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para></para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="5" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para></para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="6" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para>Go to next step.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="7" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para></para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry colname="1" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para>6.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="2" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para>Off</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="3" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para>Disconnect right spot light at circuit 64F. At 64F measure voltage to gnd.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="4" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para>64F to gnd.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="5" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para>12&#177;1.5 volts?</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="6" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para>Go to next step.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="7" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para>Locate cause of low or no voltage in circuit 64F, 64E, or 63P then repair.</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry colname="1" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para>7.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="2" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para>Off</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="3" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para>Repair or replace right spotlight and switch assembly.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="4" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para></para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="5" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para></para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="6" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para>Go to next step.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="7" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para></para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry colname="1" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para>8.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="2" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para>Off</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="3" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para>Spotlight circuits check good.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="4" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para></para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="5" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para></para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="6" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para></para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="7" morerows="0" rotate="0">
                            <para></para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
